{"tid":2097520,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法籲電訊商避用華為5G 指存在風險","createTime":"2020-07-07T01:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T11:33:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e9019a8f9b6cabaa9c31b5eec5639d8ef4cfc5","tid":2097520,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:47:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200707/HIWMNW3RLCC3ONDB7PZZJUF4WU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200707%2FHIWMNW3RLCC3ONDB7PZZJUF4WU%2F&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEqCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=39524c7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200707%2FHIWMNW3RLCC3ONDB7PZZJUF4WU%2F&h=d780e3c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200707/HIWMNW3RLCC3ONDB7PZZJUF4WU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n法籲電訊商避用華為5G 指存在風險<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GtqLn0BojGomKfxd3sCNGHIc1yQ=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EJEQYMPAGS2DQVBKHKSTNRIUVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGtqLn0BojGomKfxd3sCNGHIc1yQ%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEJEQYMPAGS2DQVBKHKSTNRIUVY.jpg&h=74d18b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n華為在歐洲市場再受挫。<br />\n<br />\n中國電訊設<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n避免使用華為5G設備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱非與中國為敵<br />\n<br />\n這是繼英國被指最快今年內將境內5G網絡逐步淘汰華為技術後，另一個不利華為拓展歐洲5G設備市場的消息。法國國家網絡安全局（ANSSI）局長普帕爾（Guillaume Poupard）接受《迴聲報》（Les Echos）訪問時表示，已經選用華為設備的公司，當局會給予三至八年的授權期限。他指出，由下周起，申請使用華為設備建設5G網絡的營辦商，若不獲得明確授權，在法定最後限期仍未獲回覆，可視申請已被拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n普帕爾解釋，作出該項決定，是要維護法國的獨立性，並非與中國為敵：「不是要針對華為，也不是反華種族主義，只是歐洲供應商與非歐洲供應商風險有別。」<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅昨在例行記者會上指出，法國曾表明不會排除華為，促請法國秉持客觀公正態度，作出獨立自主的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n此外，英國數碼、文化、媒體及體育大<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n英國正評估有關的决定。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"9d735e0f50994a681b89fc438128747eee068ab2","tid":2097520,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:48:05.000Z","msg":"強制啦。仆街"},{"pid":"31812f8613b6348c5dde1361b3c53951e2a85962","tid":2097520,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d735e0f50994a681b89fc438128747eee068ab2","tid":2097520,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:48:05.000Z","msg":"強制啦。仆街"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:48:56.000Z","msg":"美國自己都未做<br />\n叫歐洲盟友做"},{"pid":"aaf9a3d6044abce911f9f73e3e74b29258336370","tid":2097520,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31812f8613b6348c5dde1361b3c53951e2a85962","tid":2097520,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d735e0f50994a681b89fc438128747eee068ab2","tid":2097520,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:48:05.000Z","msg":"強制啦。仆街"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:48:56.000Z","msg":"美國自己都未做<br />\n叫歐洲盟友做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:50:21.000Z","msg":"美國禁哂啦。"},{"pid":"a1f84a376ce4295914f9e67a168d35977a37bc73","tid":2097520,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"仲評估 諗下到時會唔會威脅你 就知唔應該用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa519e5bd8f028e1bc54c6e469921dee703aed47","tid":2097520,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:51:24.000Z","msg":"法國仲有無石頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfb6caccc20a2166b158e6d7f45120d77302072","tid":2097520,"uid":342527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31812f8613b6348c5dde1361b3c53951e2a85962","tid":2097520,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d735e0f50994a681b89fc438128747eee068ab2","tid":2097520,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:48:05.000Z","msg":